{"tid":1405972,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"遊擊戰係一個唔錯的計劃","createTime":"2019-08-04T11:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T11:53:32.000Z","uid":260616,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"482fb0eeeb7d6abe548dbd3902ef332af999823f","tid":1405972,"uid":260616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:46:42.000Z","msg":"建基終我的中學FRD要上去前線幫手，我忍唔住要提出下意見<br />\n我覺得硬碰硬我地此終唔夠班FullGear的狗狗黎<br />\n現在我地的情況係 前線一直卑班黑警消耗緊<br />\n留守唔係一個好好的方法<br />\n只會卑班警狗捉9班義士，到時我地前線的人就會好少，好容易會輸<br />\n<br />\n相反，我地有的係行動力<br />\n如果我地做完一區 ，<br />\n等班狗狗SEt 好晒野之後，我地馬上轉區做<br />\n班黑警防線會無用，而且好難追9我地<br />\nBe water<br />\n不但可以做多D 區，卑多D 人知 （好似琴日黃大仙今）<br />\n而且警9都好難捉到我地，減少前線被捉的機會<br />\n<br />\nBeWater ，撤退唔代表我地驚，而係更聰明地保留戰力，進行下一次的行動<br />\n麻煩各位巴抗絲打 幫手推推<br />\n我唔想見到有義士受傷卑人捉<br />\n我地會成功 BE Water"},{"pid":"bee40f6159fbf872e3fd904863f0cf88eab1a14a","tid":1405972,"uid":260616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:46:55.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a7dec5fef1ef2e54133602d962fe89313c10988d","tid":1405972,"uid":260616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:47:05.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b0e829dff49c503c7abecc69b1048f65bb2b4397","tid":1405972,"uid":260616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:47:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ea10045ab782ca13dad46be597bdc30d3fcf8251","tid":1405972,"uid":260616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:47:25.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a87bf8231938a415f7891c9755b9234df445f9fc","tid":1405972,"uid":260616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:47:35.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6b6e1bcf112a184af6864a37e8dbbf93d4fc0524","tid":1405972,"uid":260616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:47:45.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3793bd989c7f4d53ec455adaf3afd52dbe9d2498","tid":1405972,"uid":260616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:47:55.000Z","msg":